resources.string: 1. The borrower is fully responsible for the safety of the equipment borrowed. \ n 2. All borrowed equipment MUST be returned on the due date. \ n 3. Dirty equipment must be cleaned before being returned. \ n 4. Borrowers must report in writing in the event of damage or loss of equipment lent to the Sports Center. \ n 5. Delay in returning borrowed equipment will incur a fine of RM 1.00 per day.
